solution: ```class Solution {
    public String concatHex36(int n) {
        int square = n * n;
        int cube = square * n;
        String hex = Integer.toString(square, 16).toUpperCase();
        String base36 = Integer.toString(cube, 36).toUpperCase();
        return hex + base36;
    }
}```
